remium care. This facility features spacious exercise zones, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care. Their...\\\",\\\"address\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"PostalAddress\\\",\\\"addressLocality\\\":\\\"Greensboro\\\",\\\"addressRegion\\\":\\\"NC\\\",\\\"addressCountry\\\":\\\"US\\\"},\\\"image\\\":\\\"/images/parks/northcarolina/rising-star-canine-ranch/rising-star-canine-ranch-1.jpg\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":9,\\\"item\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"SportsActivityLocation\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sally-said-so-dog-training-greensboro\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Sally Said So Dog Training Greensboro\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sally-said-so-dog-training-greensboro\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Sally Said So Dog Training Greensboro serves the Greensboro pet community with dedication. This facility features spacious exercise zones, caring and attentive team members, offering pet care. Their...\\\",\\\"address\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"PostalAddress\\\",\\\"addressLocality\\\":\\\"Greensboro\\\",\\\"addressRegion\\\":\\\"NC\\\",\\\"addressCountry\\\":\\\"US\\\"},\\\"image\\\":\\\"/images/parks/northcarolina/sally-said-so-dog-training-greensboro/sally-said-so-dog-training-greensboro-1.jpg\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":10,\\\"item\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"SportsActivityLocation\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sit-means-sit-dog-training-greensboro\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Sit Means Sit Dog Training Greensboro\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/sit-means-sit-dog-training-greensboro\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"North Carolina pet parents in Greensboro choose Sit Means Sit Dog Training Greensboro for premium care. This facility features climate-controlled facilities for North Carolina's varied weather,...\\\",\\\"address\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"PostalAddress\\\",\\\"addressLocality\\\":\\\"Greensboro\\\",\\\"addressRegion\\\":\\\"NC\\\",\\\"a