are. Their services ensures your dog stays comfortable year-round in North Carolina. easily accessible from Greensboro's main areas. Experience the difference at Abbott's Groom & Board\",\"slug\":\"abbotts-groom-board\",\"address\":\"1331-B Wiley Lewis Rd\",\"street\":\"1331-B Wiley Lewis Rd\",\"city\":\"Greensboro\",\"state\":\"NC\",\"zipCode\":\"27406\",\"full_address\":\"1331-B Wiley Lewis Rd, Greensboro, NC 27406, USA\",\"latitude\":36.0141253,\"longitude\":-79.7339981,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJo1dO0aMiU4gRfys3TjUC0eg\",\"phone\":\"(336) 370-1800\",\"website\":\"http://www.abbottsgroomandboard.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=wix_google_business_profile&utm_campaign=5663373277097828553\",\"rating\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":99,\"userRatingsTotal\":99,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:30 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:30 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:30 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:30 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:30 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 – 10:00 AM\",\"Sunday\":\"3:30 – 5:30 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/abbott-s-groom-board/abbott-s-groom-board-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/abbott-s-groom-board/abbott-s-groom-board-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJNaIB5SQDU4gRnx1YCbgzV_c\",\"name\":\"All American Pet Resorts - Greensboro\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"All American Pet Resorts - Greensboro provides dependable care for Greensboro's furry friends. This facility features spacious exercise zones, North Carolina pet care professionals, offering pet care. Their services provides essential socialization for your pet. strategically positioned in Greensboro. Call (336) 814-9758 to learn more about their services\",\"slug\":\"all-american-pet-resorts-greensboro\",\"address\":\"1680 Greenbourne Dr\",\"street\":\"1680 Greenbourne Dr\",\"city\":\"Greensboro\",\"state\":\"NC\",\"zipCode\":\"27409\",\"full_address\":\"1680 Greenbourne Dr, Greensboro, NC 27409, USA\",\"latitude\":36.132779,\"longitude\":-79.967004,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJNaIB5SQDU4gRnx1YCbgzV_c\",\"phone\":\"(336) 814-9758\",\"website\":\"https://www.allamericanpetresorts.com/greensboro/?utm_source=GMB&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=Greensboro\",\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":16,\"userRatingsTotal\":16,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/all-american-pet-resorts-greensboro/all-american-pet-resorts-greensboro-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/all-american-pet-resorts-greensboro/all-american-pet-resorts-greensboro-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJfykBcBlI3aQR6K5HJsOHOqA\",\"name\":\"All Good Dogs - K9 Training LLC\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"All Good Dogs - K9 Training LLC has earned the trust of Greensboro residents. This facility features modern training facilities, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. easily accessible from Greensboro's main areas. Discover why Greensboro pet parents choose All Good Dogs - K9 Training LLC\",\"slug\":\"all-good-dogs-k9-training-llc\",\"address\":\"5204 Fox Hunt Dr\",\"street\":\"5204 Fox Hunt Dr\",\"city\":\"Greensboro\",\"state\":\"NC\",\"zipCode\":\"27407\",\"full_ad